## PHASE 6 — Formal region + KaTeX

Move equations into `.shell-formal` (`.formal-grid` of `.eq-row`), hidden until
∑ Formal. If the source used MathJax, re-express the equations with KaTeX (`katex.render`)
and guard for KaTeX's deferred load (`if(window.katex) render(); else
window.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', render)`), per §8. If there are no
equations, drop the formal region and the `∑ Formal` button.

