## PHASE 7 — Info modal

Fill `#shell-info-modal`'s three placeholders (§9): `About: <title>`, a Source
`<dl class="shell-info-dl">` (Concept / Serves / Inquiry / Misconception — from the
source's own description if present), and a `<table class="shell-info-table">` of the
