## Output
- Write a NEW file `<original-name>-shell.html` in `shell-versions/` (or beside the
  source). **Never overwrite the original.**
- Do NOT spin up a browser or HTTP server to test. Verify statically: the extracted
  `<script>` passes `node --check`; the `Shell` IIFE is byte-identical to the
  reference; every original control ID is still present; no `{{…}}` token remains.
- End with a **CONVERSION REPORT:** (1) the framework detected and how the loop was
  rewired; (2) what markup moved where; (3) the guided-inquiry steps you authored;
  (4) an explicit line confirming **"physics/render code unchanged"**; (5) anything
  you could not do.

